Package: sdtmsyn
Type: Package
Title: Generate Synthetic SDTM Data for PK Studies
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R:
    person("Rainer", "Strotmann", , "rainer.strotmann@mailbox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Rainer Strotmann <rainer.strotmann@mailbox.org>
Description: This package includes functions to generate SDTM data for 
    typical PK studies, including the domains DM, VS, EX and PC. This data can
    be used for testing of downstream applications like provided by the the nif
    package.
